    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/c143aec1aca344fef973dc54e6f3ac98.webp?t=1769436376\" width=615 height=55 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/3df0bc01204efbf76127259743343f42.poster.avif?t=1769436376\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/3df0bc01204efbf76127259743343f42.webm?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/3df0bc01204efbf76127259743343f42.mp4?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《黑暗虫群》的背景设定在一个黑暗残酷的科幻世界，你所扮演的精英干员将在太空中最黑暗的角落执行各种危险的任务，而这些地方往往潜伏着可怕的异星传染病——“黑暗虫群”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《黑暗虫群》中，你将经常在黑暗逼仄的场景中与成群结队的虫子们作战。它们将撕咬吞噬所经之处的一切活物，绝不留情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/8bc51fce5ff6508c854f07f29e14efce.poster.avif?t=1769436376\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/8bc51fce5ff6508c854f07f29e14efce.webm?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/8bc51fce5ff6508c854f07f29e14efce.mp4?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，你并非永远孤身一人，《黑暗虫群》支持在线多人合作游玩，让你和朋友们并肩作战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每多一名队员，意味着你活下来的希望也越大，当然友军伤害可不是闹着玩的——所以请看准了再开火，好吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/523ca914e9962951f7f253bd85ecaee8.poster.avif?t=1769436376\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/523ca914e9962951f7f253bd85ecaee8.webm?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/523ca914e9962951f7f253bd85ecaee8.mp4?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《黑暗虫群》中你将面对铺天盖地朝你袭来的敌人，合理运用手上的资源和职业技能来消灭它们，灵活利用身边的地形或是队友（假如你有的话）来与它们周旋。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >总之千万别害怕，如果实在不行，咱们还可以再来一局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/11b3fb8d3394dd571bc966c5dc8261ae.poster.avif?t=1769436376\" width=616 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/11b3fb8d3394dd571bc966c5dc8261ae.webm?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/11b3fb8d3394dd571bc966c5dc8261ae.mp4?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以准备好涉足那些未知之境了吗？这一定将会是你职业生涯所经历过的最危险、最刺激的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >保护人类的边疆，摆脱毁天灭地的劫难，一切可都指望你了。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>&gt; 额外信息：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 预告片中的屏幕抖动（不必担心），可在游戏中调整。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 刺耳的扫描模式声音 &gt; 已在主要版本中修复。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >- 闪瞎眼的扫描模式视觉效果 &gt; 已在主要版本中修复。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/1d699c0d6ccecd4209116885a303b20b.poster.avif?t=1769436376\" width=628 height=362 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/1d699c0d6ccecd4209116885a303b20b.webm?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2303200/extras/1d699c0d6ccecd4209116885a303b20b.mp4?t=1769436376\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可能会体验到的部分内容（可能会有改动……希望能越改越好） :)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鲜血喷溅</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >单人游玩 + 本地与在线联机合作游玩</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >铺天盖地的恶心怪物</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 种分工明确的玩家职业（选择多种多样）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >需要运用智谋的游戏玩法，例如潜行，黑客和战术玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >程序性地图生成 - 永远不会重复游玩同一个关卡</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >半可破坏环境</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >枪械，道具，积累进度，还有各种会爆炸的家伙！</p></li></ul>",
